<script setup>
import { onMounted, ref } from 'vue';
import { stagger, spring, timeline } from "motion";

const cards = ref([]);

const animateCards = () => {
    cards.value = document.querySelectorAll(".card");
    const sequence = [
        [
            cards.value,
            { y: ["40%", "0%"], opacity: [0, 1] },
            {
                at: "-0.1",
                duration: 0.4,
                delay: stagger(0.3),
                easing: spring({ velocity: 100, stiffness: 50, damping: 10 }),
            },
        ],
    ];
    timeline(sequence);
};

onMounted(animateCards);
